    <item>
      <title>韩国人走出戒严混乱，震惊转为愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/as-koreans-emerge-from-martial-law-chaos-shock-turns-to-anger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统尹锡烈试图实施戒严，但未获成功。此举激怒了韩国民众，令这个因长期遭受独裁镇压而伤痕累累的国家陷入混乱。此后，愤怒的韩国民众开始集会反对他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/as-koreans-emerge-from-martial-law-chaos-shock-turns-to-anger</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 02:50:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾称中国船只向其船只发射水炮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/philippines-says-china-ship-fired-water-cannon-on-its-vessel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾称，一艘中国海警船向其船只发射了水炮，而一艘中国海军舰艇在有争议的南海浅滩附近采取了“危险”行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/philippines-says-china-ship-fired-water-cannon-on-its-vessel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 01:57:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国股市下跌，韩元在尹永康短暂戒严后回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/korean-won-gains-stocks-dip-after-president-s-brief-martial-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈在政治争斗中短暂宣布戒严，但数小时后又撤销戒严令，随后，韩国货币在周三早盘回升，但韩国股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/korean-won-gains-stocks-dip-after-president-s-brief-martial-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 00:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国为缓解监狱危机建设项目成本几乎翻倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/costs-almost-double-in-uk-building-program-to-ease-prison-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据支出监督机构称，英国旨在缓解监狱过度拥挤危机的监狱建设计划将延迟五年，且成本几乎是最初预算的两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/costs-almost-double-in-uk-building-program-to-ease-prison-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙要求法国议员不要推翻政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/macron-asks-french-lawmakers-not-to-topple-the-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙呼吁法国议员放下个人野心，拒绝推翻政府、让国家陷入政治动荡的投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/macron-asks-french-lawmakers-not-to-topple-the-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的缉毒局人选因新冠疫情封锁措施遭批评而退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-dea-pick-chronister-withdraws-from-consideration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普挑选的缉毒局局长查德·克罗尼斯特周二表示，他已撤回对该职位的考虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-dea-pick-chronister-withdraws-from-consideration</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 22:30:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰最高军事领导人警告中国威胁日益加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/new-zealand-s-top-solider-warns-of-growing-risks-from-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰最高军事长官表示，他对中国在南太平洋日益增强的存在感到担忧，并警告称，新西兰武装部队需要为任何突发事件做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/new-zealand-s-top-solider-warns-of-growing-risks-from-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 22:30:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普援引拜登赦免令纽约封口费案被驳回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-says-hush-money-case-must-be-tossed-citing-biden-pardon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的律师告诉法官，由于他在选举中获胜，他因在纽约收取封口费而被判的罪名必须撤销，律师辩称，候任总统遭到检察官的不公平对待。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-says-hush-money-case-must-be-tossed-citing-biden-pardon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 22:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永康在政治博弈后解除戒严令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/south-korea-s-yoon-says-on-tv-that-he-will-lift-martial-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈表示将撤销戒严令，这是他向议会的反对派屈服。就在几个小时前，他刚刚宣布实施戒严令，此举震动了市场并令其他世界领导人感到意外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/south-korea-s-yoon-says-on-tv-that-he-will-lift-martial-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 19:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
